title: Asset Listing: Add $ibBTC on ETH v1
body:
Asset Listing: Add $ibBTC on ETH v1

Intro: This is a vote to list $ibBTC on ETH v1 with a collateral factor and collateral cap.

Proposal: https://forum.cream.finance/t/proposal-whitelist-ibbtc-as-a-collateral-asset/1680

Rationale: List $ibBTC on ETH v1 market with collateral factor of 45% and collateral cap of $3M. ibBTC was developed jointly by BadgerDAO & DefiDollar.

For:
List $ibBTC on ETH v1 market with Collateral Factor: 45% and Collateral Cap: $3M.

Against:
Do nothing.
author: 0xd662fA474C0A1346a26374bb4581D1F6D3Fb2d94
